My favorite go to fish spot. This location has been around for many years. I used to just get fish here for Good Friday until i had their Salmon Filler and wooooooo. Best salmon ever. For all of 2019-current I’ve had fish about 2 times a week from here. Amazing and unique taste and flavoring used. I love the blend of Chinese options and other sides such as maduros and tostones (green and sweet plantains) my go to is tostones, fried rice and salmon filet. The owner (woman) is amazing. She makes it her business to get to know you and make sure any issue is resolved. Out of the full consistent year that Ive come here I only had 1 situation where the fish tasted a bit old. She made sure to give me a new fish and asked if she could give us anything else since our other food was cold. Very nice staff. There is another woman there that helps out and she is very attentive and fast to prepare orders. I would highly recommend if you’re in the area to get your fish from here. Awesome. Never long wait times or any issues !
